snippet.title: CHEROPHOBIA Trailer - A PSX PSYCHOLOGICAL HORROR
snippet.description:
You find yourself stranded in a forest after your car breaks down.


Enjoyed the game? The best support you can give us is through sharing it with others or, if possible, with a monetary contribution. Every contribution helps us create more games like this.  Plus, generous donors contributing over $10 will be contacted about featuring a memorial object or their painting in our next update and future Steam release.

Coming soon to steam!
